summary: What the Characters of Aggretsuko Think of the Twlight Books
title: What the Characters of Aggretsuko Think of the Twlight Books
body:
Been wanting to post this for a while but here goes!

Retsuko: Has heard of the books but never read them

Fenneko: Pretends to like the books but mocks them when no one’s looking

Haida: Is neutral for the most part

Ton: Loathes the books with a passion

Tsunoda: Read all the books, watched the movies, has a poster in her room, passionately ships Bella with Edward, a proud Twihard

Komiya: Is also a twilighter, bonds over the books with Tsunoda

Tsubone: Is probably a Twimom

Gori: Only read the first one but got bored with it

Washimi: Is not a fan

That hippo chick: I got nothing for her

summary: I had a dream about Retsuko in highschool being a good student but was always super stressed until she met this hyena dressed...
body:
I had a dream about Retsuko in highschool being a good student but was always super stressed until she met this hyena dressed like a japanese delincuent from the 80s for some reason (not Haida) who liked metal and was nice and caring to her. Then they started dating and that’s how she begun to enjoy metal

I don’t know how my mind managed to make such a compelling fanfic but now it’s my new headcanon for retsuko’s background  ¯\_(ツ)_/¯
